Praise awaits You, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* God, \w in|strong="H1732"\w* Zion; \w to|strong="H1732"\w* You \w our|strong="H1732"\w* vows \w will|strong="H7892"\w* \w be|strong="H1732"\w* fulfilled.
\w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w You|strong="H6726"\w* who listen \w to|strong="H8416"\w* prayer, all people \w will|strong="H6726"\w* come \w to|strong="H8416"\w* \w You|strong="H6726"\w*.
\w When|strong="H8085"\w* iniquities prevail \w against|strong="H8085"\w* \w me|strong="H8085"\w*, \w You|strong="H3605"\w* atone \w for|strong="H5704"\w* \w our|strong="H3605"\w* transgressions.

Blessed \w is|strong="H1697"\w* \w the|strong="H4480"\w* \w one|strong="H4480"\w* \w You|strong="H4480"\w* choose \w and|strong="H1697"\w* bring near \w to|strong="H1697"\w* dwell \w in|strong="H1697"\w* \w Your|strong="H4480"\w* courts! \w We|strong="H1697"\w* \w are|strong="H1697"\w* filled \w with|strong="H1697"\w* \w the|strong="H4480"\w* goodness \w of|strong="H1697"\w* \w Your|strong="H4480"\w* house, \w the|strong="H4480"\w* holiness \w of|strong="H1697"\w* \w Your|strong="H4480"\w* temple.

\w With|strong="H1004"\w* awesome deeds \w of|strong="H1004"\w* righteousness \w You|strong="H7126"\w* answer \w us|strong="H7646"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* God \w of|strong="H1004"\w* our salvation, \w the|strong="H7126"\w* hope \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w all|strong="H7931"\w* \w the|strong="H7126"\w* ends \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H7126"\w* earth \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H7126"\w* farthest seas.
\w You|strong="H3605"\w* formed \w the|strong="H3605"\w* mountains \w by|strong="H3605"\w* \w Your|strong="H3605"\w* power, having girded Yourself \w with|strong="H3605"\w* might.

\w You|strong="H2022"\w* stilled \w the|strong="H3559"\w* roaring \w of|strong="H2022"\w* \w the|strong="H3559"\w* seas, \w the|strong="H3559"\w* pounding \w of|strong="H2022"\w* \w their|strong="H3559"\w* waves, \w and|strong="H2022"\w* \w the|strong="H3559"\w* tumult \w of|strong="H2022"\w* \w the|strong="H3559"\w* nations.
Those who live far away fear \w Your|strong="H7623"\w* wonders; You make \w the|strong="H7623"\w* dawn \w and|strong="H3220"\w* sunset shout \w for|strong="H3220"\w* joy.

\w You|strong="H3372"\w* attend \w to|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H3372"\w* earth \w and|strong="H1242"\w* water \w it|strong="H1242"\w*; \w with|strong="H3427"\w* abundance \w You|strong="H3372"\w* enrich \w it|strong="H1242"\w*. \w The|strong="H3372"\w* streams \w of|strong="H3427"\w* God are full \w of|strong="H3427"\w* water, \w for|strong="H7442"\w* \w You|strong="H3372"\w* prepare our grain \w by|strong="H1242"\w* providing \w for|strong="H7442"\w* \w the|strong="H3372"\w* earth.

\w You|strong="H3588"\w* soak \w its|strong="H3588"\w* furrows \w and|strong="H4325"\w* level \w its|strong="H3588"\w* ridges; \w You|strong="H3588"\w* soften \w it|strong="H3588"\w* \w with|strong="H4390"\w* showers \w and|strong="H4325"\w* bless \w its|strong="H3588"\w* growth.

\w You|strong="H1288"\w* crown \w the|strong="H1288"\w* year \w with|strong="H7301"\w* \w Your|strong="H1288"\w* bounty, \w and|strong="H1288"\w* \w Your|strong="H1288"\w* paths overflow \w with|strong="H7301"\w* plenty.
\w The|strong="H8141"\w* pastures \w of|strong="H8141"\w* \w the|strong="H8141"\w* wilderness overflow; \w the|strong="H8141"\w* hills \w are|strong="H8141"\w* robed \w with|strong="H2896"\w* joy.

\w The|strong="H7491"\w* \w pastures|strong="H4999"\w* \w are|strong="H1524"\w* \w clothed|strong="H2296"\w* \w with|strong="H2296"\w* flocks, \w and|strong="H4057"\w* \w the|strong="H7491"\w* valleys \w are|strong="H1524"\w* decked \w with|strong="H2296"\w* grain. They shout in triumph; indeed, they sing.
